<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN286">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>veḷḷai veḷyāṭṭuc ceccai pōlat</l>
<l>taṉṉō raṉṉa viḷaiya riruppap</l>
<l>palarmītu nīṭṭiya maṇṭaiyeṉ ciṟuvaṉaik</l>
<l>kāṟkaḻik kaṭṭiliṟ kiṭappit</l>
<l>tūveḷ ḷaṟuvai pōrppit tilatē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>While, resembling the males of white goats,</l>
<l>young soldiers just like him sat there,</l>
<l>laying down, with bowls that were extended to many,</l>
<l>my little one on a cot from which the feet had been removed,</l>
<l>a pure white cloth was not made to cover him.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
